</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-image-wrap reveal">
      <div class="about-img-placeholder">K</div>
      <div class="about-corner tl">B.Tech CSE</div>
      <div class="about-corner br">MRIIRS, Faridabad</div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <div class="section-label">About me</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Engineer. Creator. Problem Solver.</h2>
      <p>I'm a Computer Science Engineering student at Manav Rachna International Institute of Research and Studies, driven by curiosity and a love for building things that matter.</p>
      <p>From training ML models to wiring up Arduino circuits, I enjoy the full spectrum — where software meets hardware, and where raw data becomes insight. I believe technology should be accessible, meaningful, and beautifully crafted.</p>
      <p>Beyond code, I bring strong leadership and time management to every team I'm part of, having led student projects and tech initiatives that bridge theory with real-world impact.</p>
      <div class="about-chips">
